text: Diana Taylor is the name of: * Diana Taylor (professor), professor at New York University's Tisch School of the Arts * Diana Taylor (superintendent) (born 1955), New York State Superintendent of Banks * Diana Taylor (General Hospital), a fictional character on the U.S. soap opera, General Hospital * Diana Taylor (businesswoman), lawyer, business owner, and company director from Geelong, Victoria * Diana Taylor (athlete)
title: Diana Taylor
